      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and meticulously kept, this is the one for you. Swing by and take a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
