    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L V8 with its 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. The mechanical state is impeccable; the rod bearings have been proactively serviced, and the six-speed manual transmission offers crisp, tactile gate engagement. The chassis retains its factory-fresh rigidity, supported by a pristine EDC (Electronic Damping Control) suspension and a variable M differential lock that ensures surgical power delivery. With a flawless carbon fiber roof and a concourse-level finish, this vehicle is an investment-grade example for the purist who demands peak atmospheric performance and mechanical transparency.",
