      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its deep, mirror-like finish without a single swirl mark or stone chip. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creases, while the original floor mats look untouched. Every button, dial, and electronic feature operates with factory precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous adherence to a professional maintenance schedule. This isn't just a used car; it's a preserved piece of automotive excellence, offering a tight, responsive driving experience that feels brand new. Complete with all original manuals, both keys, and a comprehensive service history folder.",
