      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 platform, featuring a naturally aspirated 4.0L V8 with individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. The longitudinal 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, tactile engagement, paired with the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque vectoring across the rear axle. The chassis remains factory-spec with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing precise rebound and compression adjustments. Meticulously maintained, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been addressed as preventative measures. The exterior finish is flawless, showing no signs of oxidation or clear coat failure, while the undercarriage remains free of any hydraulic leaks or bushing degradation. This is a turn-key, investment-grade machine for the discerning purist.",
